  "$schema": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/DjobaDELATV/seygo_data/main/schema/v1/card.json",
  "id": "5e89459c-8dcb-4731-a991-27c55953a348",
  "text": {
    "en": {
      "name": "Gagaga Girl",
      "effect": "You can target 1 \"Gagaga Magician\" you control; this card's Level becomes the current Level of that monster. An Xyz Monster that was Summoned using only this card and other \"Gagaga\" monsters as material gains this effect.\n\u25cf When it is Xyz Summoned: You can target 1 Special Summoned monster your opponent controls; its ATK becomes 0."
    },
    "fr": {
      "name": "Fille Gagaga",
      "effect": "Vous pouvez cibler 1 \"Magicien Gagaga\" que vous contr\u00f4lez ; le Niveau de cette carte devient le Niveau actuel du monstre. Un Monstre Xyz qui a \u00e9t\u00e9 Invoqu\u00e9 en utilisant uniquement cette carte et d'autres monstres \"Gagaga\" comme Mat\u00e9riel gagne cet effet.\n\u25cf Lorsqu'il est Invoqu\u00e9 par Xyz : vous pouvez cibler 1 monstre Invoqu\u00e9 Sp\u00e9cialement contr\u00f4l\u00e9 par votre adversaire ; son ATK devient 0."
    },
    "de": {
      "name": "Gagaga-M\u00e4dchen",
      "effect": "Du kannst 1 \u201eGagaga-Magier\u201c w\u00e4hlen, den du kontrollierst; die Stufe dieser Karte wird dieselbe wie die derzeitige Stufe jenes Monsters. Ein Xyz-Monster, das nur mit dieser Karte und anderen \u201eGagaga\u201c-Monstern als Material beschworen wurde, erh\u00e4lt diesen Effekt.\n\u25cf Wenn es als Xyz-Beschw\u00f6rung beschworen wird: Du kannst 1 als Spezialbeschw\u00f6rung beschworenes Monster w\u00e4hlen, das dein Gegner kontrolliert; seine ATK werden zu 0."
    },
    "it": {
      "name": "Ragazza Gagaga",
      "effect": "Puoi scegliere come bersaglio 1 \"Mago Gagaga\" che controlli; il Livello di questa carta diventa il Livello attuale di quel mostro. Un Mostro Xyz che \u00e8 stato Evocato utilizzando solo questa carta e altri mostri \"Gagaga\" come materiale guadagna questo effetto.\n\u25cf Quando viene Evocato Xyz: puoi scegliere come bersaglio 1 mostro Evocato Specialmente controllato dal tuo avversario; il suo ATK diventa 0."
    },
    "pt": {
      "name": "Garota Gagaga",
      "effect": "Voc\u00ea pode escolher 1 \"Mago Gagaga\" que voc\u00ea controla; o N\u00edvel deste card se torna o N\u00edvel atual desse monstro. Um Monstro Xyz que foi Invocado usando apenas este card e outros monstros \"Gagaga\" como mat\u00e9rias ganha este efeito.\n\u25cf Quando for Invocado por Invoca\u00e7\u00e3o-Xyz: voc\u00ea pode escolher 1 monstro que seu oponente controla que foi Invocado por Invoca\u00e7\u00e3o-Especial; o ATK dele se torna 0."
    },
    "es": {
      "name": "Chica Gagaga",
      "effect": "Puedes seleccionar 1 \"Mago Gagaga\" que controles; el Nivel de esta carta se convierte en el Nivel de ese monstruo en este momento. Un Monstruo Xyz que haya sido Invocado usando s\u00f3lo esta carta y otros monstruos \"Gagaga\" como material gana este efecto.\n\u25cf Cuando es Invocado Xyz: puedes seleccionar 1 monstruo Invocado de Modo Especial que controle tu adversario; su ATK se convierte en 0."
    },
    "ja": {
      "name": "\u30ac\u30ac\u30ac\u30ac\u30fc\u30eb",
      "effect": "\u2460\uff1a\u81ea\u5206\u30d5\u30a3\u30fc\u30eb\u30c9\u306e\u300c\u30ac\u30ac\u30ac\u30de\u30b8\u30b7\u30e3\u30f3\u300d\uff11\u4f53\u3092\u5bfe\u8c61\u3068\u3057\u3066\u767a\u52d5\u3067\u304d\u308b\u3002\u3053\u306e\u30ab\u30fc\u30c9\u306e\u30ec\u30d9\u30eb\u306f\u305d\u306e\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\u3068\u540c\u3058\u306b\u306a\u308b\u3002\u2461\uff1a\u3053\u306e\u30ab\u30fc\u30c9\u3092\u542b\u3080\u30d5\u30a3\u30fc\u30eb\u30c9\u306e\u300c\u30ac\u30ac\u30ac\u300d\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\u306e\u307f\u3092\u7d20\u6750\u3068\u3057\u3066\uff38\u53ec\u559a\u3057\u305f\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\u306f\u4ee5\u4e0b\u306e\u52b9\u679c\u3092\u5f97\u308b\u3002\u25cf\u3053\u306e\u30ab\u30fc\u30c9\u304c\uff38\u53ec\u559a\u3057\u305f\u6642\u3001\u76f8\u624b\u30d5\u30a3\u30fc\u30eb\u30c9\u306e\u7279\u6b8a\u53ec\u559a\u3055\u308c\u305f\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\uff11\u4f53\u3092\u5bfe\u8c61\u3068\u3057\u3066\u767a\u52d5\u3067\u304d\u308b\u3002\u305d\u306e\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\u306e\u653b\u6483\u529b\u3092\uff10\u306b\u3059\u308b\u3002"
